## Done

### B16 ‚Äî uir-test ordering bug
- **Status:** Done. The failure was in `esbuild-integration-test.rkt`, not `uir-test.rkt`. The test tried to parse esbuild-bundled JSX+IIFE output through the TS parser, which crashed because IIFE-wrapped JSX isn't valid TS source. Removed the pipeline-from-bundled-output tests; multi-file resolution is covered by `tsx-integration-test.rkt` (B6).
- **Files:** `racklr-test/esbuild-integration-test.rkt`

### B15 ‚Äî SSR / data fetching
- **Status:** Done. `getStaticProps` and `getServerSideProps` (including `async` variants) are stripped from page output via regex in `emit-router.rkt`.
- **Files:** `racklr/emit-router.rkt` (`page->js`), `racklr-test/tsx-integration-test.rkt` (B15 tests)
- **Details:** Regex `(?m:^(export )?(async )?function (getStaticProps|getServerSideProps)\([^)]*\) \{.*\};?\n?)` strips entire function definition after emit.

